data.description: Spectacular 3 bdrm 2 bath ranch.  Home is in a neighborhood with many mature trees. This home features soaring cathedral ceilings in the greatroom (with skylights) that let in an enormous amount of light.  The home has been well maintained and has many updates in the recent years: HVAC, roof, flooring, fencing, and paint.  The large yard will accommodate big gatherings or just spend your evenings enjoying Mother Nature from your deck or screened in patio. Home is in a neighborhood with many mature trees and also has a mini-barn storage unit on site.  This is the one.  Schedule your showing today!
